title: This One’s Gonna Do Numbers
author: VD
content_html:
THE AWAKENER movie is being released in English on January 18. It looks as if the dubbed version might be even better than the original Brazilian Portuguese version. We just found out about it, but we do intend to ensure that the comic will be available in a collector’s print edition later this month.
